---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="newsletter mx-auto">
    <!-- Intro -->
    <h1 class="page-title">Modern Compass Newsletter</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      The <em>Modern Compass</em> newsletter gives you clarity without fluff, frameworks that work,
      and stories that stick. Every issue is designed to help you navigate life with more purpose
      and focus.
    </p>

    <!-- Promo Graphic -->
    <div class="promo">
      <img src="/images/newsletter-promo.png" alt="Modern Compass newsletter promo" loading="lazy" />
    </div>

    <!-- Beehiiv Subscribe Embed -->
    <div class="newsletter-embed">
      <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
      <iframe
        src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
        class="beehiiv-embed"
        frameborder="0"
        scrolling="no"
        title="Subscribe to Modern Compass on Beehiiv"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Top Issues -->
    <section class="top-issues">
      <h2>Top Issues</h2>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <article class="flip-card">
          <button class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-face flip-front">
              <h3>Resonance &amp; The Power of Two</h3>
              <p class="kicker">Why we click with some people and not others</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-face flip-back">
              <p><strong>Snapshot:</strong> Resonance forms when two signals align. The Power of Two
                focuses attention on two meaningful commonalities that create momentum.</p>
              <p class="cta">Read the full issue →</p>
            </div>
          </button>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <article class="flip-card">
          <button class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-face flip-front">
              <h3>Creative Equity Review</h3>
              <p class="kicker">Track effort, compound wins, reduce guesswork</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-face flip-back">
              <p><strong>Snapshot:</strong> A weekly audit to measure inputs, compounding signals, 
                and directional gains so progress stays visible even when vanity metrics lag.</p>
              <p class="cta">Read the full issue →</p>
            </div>
          </button>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Subscribe (kept at bottom) -->
    <section aria-labelledby="why-subscribe" class="why max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h3 id="why-subscribe" class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-3">
        Why Subscribe to <em>Modern Compass</em>?
      </h3>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Most personal growth content is noise made up of quick tips and abstract concepts that may be difficult to approach and implement.
        <em>Modern Compass</em> is different.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base font-medium mb-2">Each issue gives you:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Clarity without fluff.</strong> Big ideas distilled into practical takeaways.</li>
        <li><strong>Proven frameworks.</strong> Tools like <em>TimeOS</em> and the <em>Intention vs. Action</em> activity to guide real decisions.</li>
        <li><strong>Action over theory.</strong> Exercises and reflections you can apply immediately.</li>
        <li><strong>Relatable depth.</strong> Stories and examples that stick, not abstract jargon.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Subscribers also get early access to tools, digital downloads, and updates on the
        <em>Modern Compass</em> book.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-900 font-medium">
        This is not about chasing endless self-improvement. It is about building the compass that helps you
        navigate life with purpose, trust, and clarity.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .promo img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .newsletter-embed {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .beehiiv-embed {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 640px;
    height: 460px;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .top-issues h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .card-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  /* Flip Cards */
  .flip-card {
    perspective: 1000px;
  }
  .flip-inner {
    width: 100%;
    height: 220px;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }
  .flip-face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: grid;
    align-content: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .flip-front h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .flip-front .kicker { color: #6b7280; }
  .flip-back { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .flip-inner:hover .flip-front,
  .flip-inner:focus-visible .flip-front { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .flip-inner:hover .flip-back,
  .flip-inner:focus-visible .flip-back { transform: rotateY(360deg); }
  .flip-back .cta { color: var(--primary-color, #0ea5e9); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
